        <p><strong>Server error or some chosen inputs are invalid at this time!</strong></p>
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x200" alt="Error Image" class="error-image">
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please feel free to <a href="mailto:support@example.com">contact our support team</a>.</p>
        <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
        <p>If you did not request this email, you can safely ignore it.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
